	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, Had to add this after the last post. The Pattern is found in Tenebrous Mountain. At the zone in from The Grimling Forest. The Grimling Runner spawns there every 90 minutes. That pack is No Drop. But you can take that and turn it in in Katta for the Pattern which is Lore only. The Perfect Owlbear Pelts will drop in Paudal Caverns and will also drop in Hollowshade Moor. If you can find the Owlbears up (With the War that can take place in that zone). Silks - Yes they are easy to get, But not in Hollowshade Moor. Never seen one drop there. They are found in Shadeweaver's Thicket. Which is on the other side of Shar Vahl. Hope this clears up what the last person posted.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
